dialogs: I can't believe I'm even trying this.
Isn't that just… insulting?
This isn't helping.
Stop.
I feel weird.
This is not calming me down.
This doesn't make any sense.
It doesn't even look good there.
That's actually very creepy.
This feels wrong.
Why am I adding more stickers?
Not very helpful.
Was this what was playing on the radio?
That was not what they looked like.
The colors are all wrong.
Nothing looks right.
I don't want to forget this.
This makes me feel worse.
I miss your voice.
Give me my grandma back.
Everything is fading.
I hate this.
Coldness is all that is left.
What would she say to all this?
It's too quiet without you.
Pain isn't going away.
I just want everyone to leave me be.
I don't want any more change.
Please let me remember.
That wasn't her face.
This smell….
I always hated hospitals.
A sticker a day…
The beeping never stops.
I can still feel the alcohol burning my nostrils.
You were so pale.
Your hand was so cold.
Doesn't that make you feel better?
Good job, buddy!
The past is what we make it to be.
The happiness of your life depends on the quality of your thoughts.
Think positive, feel positive!
One sticker at a time!
Sad thoughts, begone!
Sadness has no chance against you!
Stick, laugh, love!
No happiness without action.
Everything is better with stickers!
Oh how unpleasant, glad you covered that up.
Don't forget to check out the limited-time GRIEF collection!
Sadness, now 100% off!
Now that would put a smile on any face.
Let the sparkle out!
Stick it to the bad memories.
I can already feel the positivity!
The more colors, the better you feel, now isn't that fun?
Smile through sadness, that'll teach 'em!
Don't let depression win, glam it up!
What matters is how YOU remember things.
Is it just me or is it getting happy in here?
Just perfect.
Remember to rate the app and make ME happy!
Don't forget to check out our Mental Health Day special discount!
More stickers = more giggles
That looks SO GOOD on there!
Only important emotions are the sparkly ones
See how it's much better like that?
Don't think, act!
Paint the picture you want to see!
Remember how ugly things were a minute ago? Well, you really shouldn't!
You're a natural!
A sticker a day, keeps the bad thoughts away.
Oh I see what you're doing!
Check out our new app Careful Whispers and get them sweet affirmations!
Have you taken a walk lately?
That's what I call a pleasant memory, good job!
You are being very brave right now.
Can you hear them? Everyone's hearts?
You were not the first to spill tears here. Neither the last.
She kept looking for you. To the last moment.
Silence is the foe of life.
Laying there…So still…
Are the eyes kind? Do they look like they're crying?
